    <cas:Sofa xmi:id="1" sofaNum="1" sofaID="_InitialView" mimeType="text" sofaString="Two (2) new confirmed cases were reported today; one (1) case each from Damaturu and Nguru LGAs. The total number of confirmed COVID-19 case(s) remains forty-nine (49): Twenty (20) cases from Damaturu, eleven (11) cases from Nguru, nine (9) cases from Bade, three (3) cases from Potiskum, and one (1) case each from Geidam, Tarmuwa, Bursari, Fika, Gulani and Gujba LGAs  Total confirmed case(s) of COVID-19 amongst Health Care Workers (HCWs) in the state is thirteen (13): Seven (7) nurses, four (4) doctors, one (1) physiotherapist, and one (1) laboratory scientist  The total number of deaths due to COVID-19 in the state is six (6)"/>
